    "data": [
        {
            "title": "【紅磡新盤】首岸1期開售前添食120伙｜折實均呎20,886元｜同柱最高實際加幅僅1.81%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒地牽頭發展的紅磡庇利街項目首岸第1期推售步伐持續。發展商上周六（25日）首輪開售218伙前夕，於上周五（24日）晚率先公布第3號價單，加推120伙。這批單位折實平均呎價為20,886元，對比上一張價單雖上調約4.74%，不過，若比較同座同柱單位，實際加幅僅介乎0.42%至1.81%，反映發展商是次屬原價加推。上述120伙將於周四（30日）全數作次輪發售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首岸第1期價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首岸第1期價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4swq7yQ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首岸第1期價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首岸第1期原價加推120伙｜折實均呎19,940元｜同柱單位加幅約1.28%至3.79%\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首岸第1期原價加推120伙｜折實均呎19,940元｜同柱單位加幅約1.28%至3.79%;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4mPjzdj\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首岸第1期原價加推120伙｜折實均呎19,940元｜同柱單位加幅約1.28%至3.79%</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c573e321-f985-354f-bd88-4f140a04d18f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tWfy9z\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>發展商加推120伙 折實均呎約20,886元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首岸第1期於上周五（24日）公布第3號價單，加推120伙。新一批單位涵蓋106伙兩房戶、7伙兩房連平台特色戶，以及7伙三房戶，實用面積介乎301至642平方呎。按定價計算，整批單位總市值約10.92億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商維持提供最高9%折扣優惠。是次加推單位的折實售價介乎684.5萬至1,399.85萬元，折實呎價為19,121至23,742元。整批單位的折實均呎為20,886元，較第2號價單的19,940元高約4.74%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於折實均呎有所提升，主要是由於這批單位以高層為主，並包含B室、Q室及平台特色戶，整體景觀與戶型分布均與首批單位不同。若與同柱單位比較，實際售價相差不大，僅輕微加價，屬原價加推。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房折實684.5萬元入場</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房入場單位為第2座15樓L室，實用面積339平方呎，折實售價約684.5萬元，折實呎價約20,192元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7pqgoL5SlNtT1.uKaVkEYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/3a123ff12797a36d63f2a432d63c9ce0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房入場單位：第2座15樓L室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>三房折實1,339.61萬元入場</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三房入場單位為第2座22樓A室，實用面積642平方呎，折實售價約1,339.61萬元，折實呎價約20,866元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_8fkTq2XRce8LHvhx.aukw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/832ce7fbc174d11c003af5be6ceb93c2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>三房入場單位：第2座22樓A室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>折實呎價介乎1.91萬至2.37萬餘元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在這批單位中，折實呎價最低為第2座21樓H室兩房戶，實用面積399平方呎，折實售價約762.94萬元，折實呎價19,121元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於折實呎價最高的單位，為第2座3樓K室兩房連平台特色戶，實用面積301平方呎，折實售價約714.62萬元，折實呎價23,742元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>比較同柱單位 實際加幅僅約0.42%至1.81%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然第3號價單的整體折實均呎較上一張價單高約4.74%，但主要是由於這批單位以高層為主，並涵蓋不同室號及連平台特色戶，因而拉高整體均呎。若直接比較同柱單位，實際加幅僅約0.42%至1.81%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以第3號價單的第2座22樓A室為例，折實呎價為20,866元；對比第2號價單中同柱的21樓A室，其折實呎價為20,494元，兩者僅相差約1.81%。若計及樓層及景觀因素，發展商是次定價屬原價加推。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rUO_TcmExlZoh95uuhFbCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/f617494b71638cd787c1b4ff4294fecb\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>3號與2號價單比較：第2座22樓與21樓A室</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>周二截票 周四開售</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商於周日（26日）公布最新銷售安排，定於周四（30日）展開次輪銷售，推售上述120伙，並於周二（28日）下午4時截止登記。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目簡介與周邊配套</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由恒基兆業、希慎興業、帝國集團及市建局合作發展的首岸第1期，位於紅磡庇利街1號。項目合共提供360伙，實用面積由301至642平方呎不等，全數為兩房至三房戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目距離港鐵土瓜灣站約8分鐘步程。校網隸屬小學35網，中學屬於九龍城區。項目預計關鍵日期為2027年8月31日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/首岸-33812\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首岸</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/九龍城-27371\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">九龍城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"土瓜灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:土瓜灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/土瓜灣-27389\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">土瓜灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紅磡\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:紅磡;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/紅磡-27387\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">紅磡</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4-%E9%A6%96%E5%B2%B81%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%94%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%B7%BB%E9%A3%9F120%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E20-886%E5%85%83-%E5%90%8C%E6%9F%B1%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E5%8A%A0%E5%B9%85%E5%83%851-81-75723\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4-%E9%A6%96%E5%B2%B81%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%94%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%B7%BB%E9%A3%9F120%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E20-886%E5%85%83-%E5%90%8C%E6%9F%B1%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E5%8A%A0%E5%B9%85%E5%83%851-094242076.html",
